## Installation

1. Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/devops-ai-agent.git

2. Move into project directory

cd devops-ai-agent

3. Install dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt

## Run the Project

uvicorn app.main:app --reload

